channel.title: Anti Syi Program
channel.description:
Download link: http://uppit.com/FQUPOS http://uppit.com/FQUPOS
Hey guys it's Cerda the owner of google moparscape staff banned me, Oh well i'm just here to release my last piece of work dedicated to the people that are having trouble with Syi - The nulling program
What SYI does? syi logs nulls into your server until it laggs out and crashes, however what if you were to allow only 1 connect per ip therefore all the nulls logging in will be blocked because their already is one online. this will work with every Source as it's a program you use with your run.bat.
So now the shit czar Sources have protection against SYI, this will make your server syi proof.
[b]How the program Works?[/b] Once you download it click the File that says: Anti syi - Use this one Once you have opened it, it will be a green box, click the "browse" Button Find your Server Files, then Find run.bat, click it and congratulations your server is running, the program only allows 1 connection per ip address onto the server, if you need to use a re-starter click the Auto re-starter button in the bottom right hand corner of the box, you can select 10,15,20,25,30,35,40,45 Minutes. I'll probably be banned soon seeing how the staff hate me here, well anyway Enjoy this program It took me around 1 week to make it :P
Download link: http://uppit.com/FQUPOS http://uppit.com/FQUPOS
